# LiveRubber Project Rules

## Architecture Overview
- Structure: Monorepo (Turborepo + Bun).
- Frameworks: React Native (Mobile), Node.js (Service).
- Design Pattern: Clean Architecture (Handler -> Service -> Repository -> Domain).
- Database: SQLite (local).

## AI & Privacy
- Local Agents: Use Ollama/DeepSeek for PII (Personally Identifiable Information).
- Cloud Agents: Use Gemini Flash for generic logic (anonymized data only).
- Connectivity: Always use Model Context Protocol (MCP) to bridge LLMs to SQLite.

## Coding Standards
- Language: TypeScript with strict typing.
- Linting/Formatting: Biome.
- State Management: Jotai (Mobile).
- Data Fetching: TanStack Query.

## Contextual Hints
- Domain logic is always in `apps/service/src/internal/domain`.
- Shared types reside in `packages/shared/@types`.